{"items":[{"id":"942443","user":{"id":"706012","nickname":"害羞的独角蛛907","avatar_url":"https://static-user-center.codemao.cn/user_0001.png","subject_id":795,"work_shop_name":"小螃蟹编程","work_shop_level":1,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>挖坟！考古！洛阳铲安排上！（贴号1516，本年首次开挖）</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1614167128,"created_at":1614167128,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"7524","user":{"id":"148883","nickname":"活动喵","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/nemo/ryc-BqCbv.jpeg","subject_id":228,"work_shop_name":"编程猫官方","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>如果能把具体要实现的效果，或者作品做个介绍，这样会好很多；你所指的角色是自动运动的么？还是需要玩家操作的？<br><br>如果是前者，可以直接划线为界，判断碰到线的颜色时调转角度；（当然一楼的做法也可以~）；</p>\n<p>如果是后者，就必须的用1楼的做法了，详细说来的话，是在每一个含有角色操作命令的事件，加上一个角色坐标判断，判断其是否在你所限定的区域里，是则执行操作命令，否这操作无效。<br><br>如果没能解决问题，可以继续讨论哈~</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/2.gif\"></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1480778931,"created_at":1480778931,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"7481","user":{"id":"147531","nickname":"浪日子的鲸","avatar_url":"https://creation.codemao.cn//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfMTQ3NTMxXzBfMTY2ODY3NDIxNzUxMF9IYUVhNGc4Mw==.jpg","subject_id":22534,"work_shop_name":"技术喵爱小鱼干","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>判断当角色的x，y超过多少时，侦测里面有角色的x，y值</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1480728715,"created_at":1480728715,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":3,"counted":true}